div.div:
Tokens are locked in NFT credited to user until the amount if $TT equals or exceeds the value of assets in the bonded LP tokens.
This value is calculated by using the TT / TDT and TDT / T1, TDT / T2 markets as price oracles to calculate the TWAP.
TWAP calculations are used to protect against flash loan attacks.
Once the value of the bonded $TT equals the value of the LP tokens, any overage of $TT may be withdrawn or used in other pools.
The bonded LP tokens are not available for other uses. This allows a user to use this process to secure liquidity in the vault to ensure their position will maintain underlying liquidity for future usage of their $TT.
